credit_line: Gift of Stephen W. Brener and Carol B. Brener
title: Brown Agate
provenance: Collection of Carol B. Brener and Stephen W. Brener
description: Cylinder in form, single piece of brown agate with white striations, hollowed out to form box; capped with silver collar, silver lid attached to collar, hinged at back; fine band of twisted silver wire wraps around the perimeter of lid's edge, flower with petals of twisted wire at lid's center. Striker carved into stone on bottom.
name: Matchsafe
